      "review_summary": "The branch changes stale native hook direct-bridge errors to fall through to gateway RPC, changes Codex app-server native relay invocation failures to before_tool_call policy fallback, and updates focused tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +1, Tests -13. Total -12 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: Partially: current source and tests show the stale direct-bridge and app-server relay failure paths hard-deny on main. I did not run the reported WSL2/Docker gateway restart or drain sequence against this PR head.",
